{"type": "article", "id": 23446, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-08T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 24531, "name": "Munkii"}, {"id": 24532, "name": "Prepd"}, {"id": 24533, "name": "Alan Hughes"}, {"id": 18314, "name": "Luis Arrivillaga"}, {"id": 24534, "name": "Lera Moiseeva"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607141233yRerikAuXCHKp3sE.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>Ceiba by Luis Arrivillaga</h2>\n<p>这是一个可旋转的衣架，由危地马拉设计师 Luis Arrivillaga 为意大利品牌 Living Divani 设计。沿着中轴可以依次打开四个小框，以任意一个点做支撑，由高到低，有简单几何图形感。开合方便也有助于适应不同形状的墙面并将它收到墙边。衣架由橡木制作，有原色或黑色。<a href=\"http://arrivillagabasile.com\">有兴趣可以点击工作室链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152907WHxuq7BQkznv1NfS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86969253\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152907Aln7bE25zRTaOiDK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152907GiT2aZLhJHNPpwVj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152908rxJY53WFqvQcfAHX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24450952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152908TqeQn3rbMiNgOs8F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Ray chair by Lera Moiseeva </h2>\n<p class=\"\">这把椅子来自俄罗斯女设计师 Lera Moiseeva，它的颜色和形态都指向生长中的植物。座位下面的“腿”朝着五个不同的方向，就像植物的根。圆形座位上连接着弯曲的钢铁座位靠背，让椅子显得轻盈。它是在“建立自然和设计之间的对话”题目下的设计，有墨绿色、黑色和白色三种，<a href=\"http://leramoiseeva.com/RAY-CHAIR\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152909RUSfX4DZxVEvoplm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071529099uk8iF0RsMbxqcmv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152910qzg3Pv21aFJQp46n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00106838\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152910UYO05DTpFtNsPhvQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152911IZT3DFwcE4A2RNxQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Alpha&amp;Beta by Munkii</h2>\n<p>这盏台灯有一个有趣的名字 Alpha&amp;Beta，灯的底座相连而灯头分离，很有情景感，似乎象征了人和人之间的关系。灯头的朝向角度并不一致，因而这盏灯也不是完全对称的，可以进行多种解读。灯的底座用 Polycarbonate（聚碳酸酯）材料制作，可以选择黑、白、金三种颜色。设计方来自新加坡的一个成立于 2006 年设计品牌  Munkii，<a href=\"http://www.munkii.com.sg/alpha-beta-dimension.html\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152911wXLSPgHtaRMdl1mN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071529128gJ6p3XzQLnYe0uB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071529123Yb5Xz8Bg97rVu6t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152913x8oQ6cL1RgnM5lUF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060715291394Kn8AMuVGH0dZCB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Prep Pack by Prepd </h2>\n<p>这是一个可携带的木质饭盒，它另配有不同型号的保温盒，相应的 Prepd App 提供健康食谱的意见，指导你购买食物。当你按照食谱准备时，就能得到相应的热能计算，方便减法人士控制饮食。木质的盖子滑动下来，也可作为吃饭的垫子。刀叉等餐具都带磁铁，以便更好地固定在饭盒里。产品目前还在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/prepd-pack-the-lunchbox-reimagined#/\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152913k1fMbUSWKihVxYTv.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152914CyX76zokAREYfbnw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152915fwkA3aNimIKDWUn8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152915OdIqukDzo8VwrG0J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071529159cmjWkG4SHawJXAN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57205882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>FIELD GOOD by 永塚</h2>\n<p>这是一组家用花园铲，由日本永塚制作所设计，采用金属加工工艺制成。春天是耕种的季节，他们希望能让人们感受到家庭园艺的乐趣。农铲分成“in、on、above”三个系列色，浅色系代表紫阳花和波斯菊等各种花朵，适合女性和高龄者使用；深色表现土地和蔬菜的颜色；矿物色则指代金银铜。铲子的重量很轻，在 45g 到 220g 之间。售价 900 日元起，<a href=\"http://www.eizuka-ss.com/field-good-%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E3%82%A2/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152916WgtSlXb41h3orYEH.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7027027\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152917LPrw0HKmxj1bXSgD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152917Ehe4OfPgD0Ky2svz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152918IuU5PzQ2RA89SvCB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071529185CXGQfVIcawgDt3K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2027027\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Noble &amp; Savage by Alan Hughes</h2>\n<p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">这组茶叶包装使用了非常亮丽的蓝色，长方体的盒子后面用文件袋一样的扣子连接，体现出古典和精致。封面上以白底黑字的形式标注信息，有银色的花体字，增加了光泽感，也让人联想起精装书。Noble &amp; Savage 是一个初创的品牌，他们强调茶叶的健康和优良品质。</span></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152919NlDOeutZwsVnmWyM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152919vYynxPso7kTzIWGN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152920jhcRoYL5G4fMU01s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152920Z04GWAcPhJgz819d.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152921zEUKnPj7bHZ2RkGF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152921URDvtPdb0o5Z3yex.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n\n"}